	<div class="Intro Container Container--full Container--centered u-textAlignCenter">
		<h1 class="Intro-title">
			<span class="Intro-radio">Radio</span>
			<span class="Intro-4000">4000</span>
		</h1>
		<p class="Intro-slogan">A single channel for everyone<br>and an infinity of great tracks curated with love.</p>
	</div>
</section>

<div class="Sections">

	<section class="Section">
		<div class="Container u-push--1">
			<a href="https://github.com/Internet4000/radio4000-manifest" class="Muted" target="_blank">
				The Radio4000 manifest (v0.1)<br>
				March 12, 2016<br>
				Berlin
			</a>
		</div>
		<div class="Container Container--centered">
			<h1 class="u-push--1"><small>Introduction, about</small> humans and algorithms</h1>
			<p>We believe each of us are engaged on a musical journey, sonic exploration of the available spectrum of sounds.</p>
			<p>We, Humans, select music according to our taste. Because it makes us dance, smile, think, not think, forget; because we like it or we think it's interesting. This is something computers can't do, even though they gave us the internet.</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="Section Section--80vh Section--bg Section--bgFixed"
				style="background-image: url('assets/images/illustrations/the-sounds-of-earth-record-cover.jpg')">
		<span class="Section-bgCredits">
			<a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:The_Sounds_of_Earth_Record_Cover_-_GPN-2000-001978.jpg" target="_blank">
				The Sounds of Earth Record Cover<br>
				NASA/JPL
			</a>
		</span>
	</section>

	<section class="Section">
		<div class="Container Container--centered">
			{{!-- <article class="MediaBlock">
				<div class="MediaBlock-body"> --}}
					<h1 class="u-push--1"><small>On Radio4000</small> everyone <small>has</small> one radio<small>, only one</small></h1>
