	<section class="Section">
		<div class="Container Container--full">
			<div class="Grid Grid--center Grid--firstHidden">
				{{#each model.featured as |item|}}
				<div class="Grid-cell">
					{{channel-card channel=item}}
				</div>
				{{/each}}
				<div class="Grid-cell">
					<div class="ChannelCard ChannelCard--text">
						<p>Simply tap a channel to play it!</p>
						<p>Each channel is as unique as the person who crafted it</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="Section Section--80vh Section--bg Section--bgFixed"
				style="background-image: url('assets/images/illustrations/bernal-construction-nasa-ames-research-center.jpg')">
		<span class="Section-bgCredits">
			<a href="http://settlement.arc.nasa.gov/70sArtHiRes/70sArt/art.html" target="_blank">
				Torus Construction<br>
				NASA Ames Research Center
			</a>
		</span>
	</section>

	<section class="Section">
		<div class="Container Container--center Container--full">
			<h1 class="u-push--1"><small>Radio4000 is a music</small> tool <small>and<br></small> a service</h1>
			<div class="Grid">
				<figure class="Grid-cell">
					<a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:%27Around_the_Moon%27_by_Bayard_and_Neuville_21.jpg">
						<img src="assets/images/illustrations/around-the-moon-bayard-neuville.jpg" alt="" />
					</a>
				</figure>
				<figure class="Grid-cell">
					<a href="http://pip.tamil.fr/bib/31188" class="Muted">
						<img src="assets/images/illustrations/une-caverne-pendant-la-nuit-a-l-epoque-du-grand-ours-et-du-mammouth-emile-bayard.jpg" alt="" />
					</a>
				</figure>
				<article class="Grid-cell">
					<h2>
						<small>A service </small>for and by humans.
					</h2>
					<p>
						The music content on radio4000 is only generated by Humans who want to share their music selection.
						You can give yourself some rest in music digging and listen to what's around you.
						Discover some crazy tracks in the context of someone you like the taste of.
					</p>
				</article>
				<article class="Grid-cell Grid-cell--double">
					<h2>
						<small>A tool to</small> understand <small>your music discoveries.</small>
					</h2>
					<p>
						We want to provide you with some context for your music history. For example what genre it is, which label it was released on and when it came out.
						That way you'll have a better chance to dig into fresh discoveries.
					</p>
				</article>
				<article class="Grid-cell">
					<h2>
						<small>A tool to</small> manage <small>your online music.</small>
					</h2>
					<p>
						All those links pointing to music you like are now stored somewhere.
					</p>
				</article>
				<figure class="Grid-cell Grid-cell--double">
					<a class="Muted" href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Georg_Abraham_Hackert_-_Ruins_of_the_Augustan_Bridge_at_Narni_-_WGA11015.jpg">
						<img src="assets/images/illustrations/ruins-of-the-augustus-bridge-at-narni-view-1-georg-abraham-hackert.jpg" alt="" />
					</a>
				</figure>
				<article class="Grid-cell Grid-cell--double">
					<h2>
						<small>A service </small>to extend discoveries.
					</h2>
					<p>
						Everyone can access your radio channel and listen to your selection. Anytime, anywhere.
						But no one needs to know who you are, it is only about music.<br>
						Aliases are cool.
					</p>
				</article>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="Section">
		<div class="Container Container--full">
			<h1 class="u-push--1"><small>What Radio4000</small> stands for</h1>
			<div class="Grid">
				<article class="Grid-cell">
					<h2><small>Cultural</small> diversities</h2>
					<p>
						Diferences of taste and personalities are the core of Radio4000. We value and respect plurality of self expressions.
					</p>
				</article>
				<article class="Grid-cell">
					<h2><small>Fair </small>ecosystem</h2>
					<p>
						A platform such as Radio4000 can only exist because people create and share their music.<br>
						Let's work on a fair and viable ecosystem leading to more music and more sharing.<br>
					</p>
				</article>
				<article class="Grid-cell">
					<h2>Privacy <small>and</small> ownership</h2>
					<p>
						As we said, no one needs to know who you are, Radio4000 neither.
						The only data we save about you is what's in your radio channel.
						Also you can export all your music, what's yours' yours.
					</p>
				</article>
				<article class="Grid-cell">
					<h2><small>Embrace the</small> future</h2>
					<p>
						We're all here to imagine and create a music experience for year 4000
					</p>
				</article>
				<figure class="Grid-cell">
					<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:More_otho_flying.JPG" class="Muted">
						<img src="assets/images/illustrations/more-otho-flying-richard-neuhauss.jpg" alt="" />
					</a>
				</figure>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="Section Section--100vh Section--bg Section--bgFixed Section--flex"
				style="background-image: url('assets/images/illustrations/karnak-william-henry-goodyear.jpg')">
		<span class="Section-bgCredits">
			<a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:S10.08_Karnak,_image_9922.jpg" target="_blank">
				Karnak<br>
				William Henry Goodyear
			</a>
		</span>
	</section>

	<section class="Section Section--flex">
		<div class="Section-inner Section-inner--vCentered Container Container--full u-push--1">
			<h1 class="u-push--1 u-textAlignCenter">Explore <small>or</small> share <small>music<br> on Radio4000</small></h1>
			<div class="Grid Grid--center">
				<div class="Grid-cell">
					{{channel-card channel=model.featured.firstObject}}
				</div>
				<div class="Grid-cell Muted">
					<p>This channel is called <strong>{{model.featured.firstObject.title}}</strong>.</p>
					<p>Because the human behind can only have one channel, there's nowhere for the good music to hide. Highs and lows, ebbs and flows, Cambodian funk and techno. Each mix is exactly that — a mix.</p>
					<p>Click on the channel card to start exploring it.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="Grid-cell">
					<div class="Intro-actions">
						{{#link-to 'channels' class="Btn Btn--huge" title="Discover music by channels"}}
						Discover radios
						{{/link-to}}
						{{#if session.currentUser.channels.firstObject}}
							{{#link-to 'channel' session.currentUser.channels.firstObject class="Btn Btn--important Btn--huge" title="Your radio"}}
							Go to your “{{session.currentUser.channels.firstObject.title}}”
							{{/link-to}}
						{{else}}
							{{#link-to 'channels.new' class="Btn Btn--important Btn--huge" title="Continue to create your radio"}}
							Create your radio
							{{/link-to}}
						{{/if}}
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>


	</section>
</div>
